## ğŸ—‚ï¸ **Database Schema**

```javascript
// User Schema
{
  name: String,
  email: String,
  bloodType: String,
  donationHistory: [ObjectId],
  healthRecords: Object,
  location: GeoPoint
}

// Donation Centers
{
  name: String,
  location: GeoPoint,
  availableSlots: [Date],
  contactInfo: Object,
  facilities: [String]
}

// Appointments
{
  donorId: ObjectId,
  centerId: ObjectId,
  appointmentDate: Date,
  status: String,
  remindersSent: Boolean
}
```

